'''Inner Uvena''' was an area of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Uvena Prime/Legends|Uvena Prime]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

The [[Shistavanen/Legends|Shistavanens]], native of the planet Uvena Prime, presented bright yellow eyes when they were from the Inner Uvena area, as exemplified by [[Yurdak Fav]].<ref name="AIR" />

